Homepage: http://www.logilab.org/projects/projman
Description: tool for project management
 projman is a tool used for managing projects and creating reports,
 such as project costs, resource usages, Gantt diagram and resources
 activities diagram.
 It includes the following functionnalties:
  * scheduling of a project
  * managing work-groups' actvities
  * Gantt diagrams generation
  * resources' usage diagrams generation
  * generation of xml doc (under docbook dtd) to list tasks, evaluate costs
 .
 All different format and output are XML files.
 .

